data.project_title: AddLidar – Airborne Laser Scanner Data Repository and Processing Portal for the ARES Observatory
data.project_abstract: This project aims to establish an open database and processing pipeline for ALS (Airborne Laser Scanner) data, complementing the imaging spectrometry platform, to promote transparency, accessibility, reproducibility and innovation in sensor co-registration and data analysis, ultimately benefiting scientific communities worldwide.

work_packages.wp_title: Preparation and coordination with the ARES community
Setup of the online viewer and data browsing interface
